snippet: The Jets have capitalized on running back Bilal Powell’s ability to produce while giving Shonn Greene a breather, especially in the final month of the regular season.
lead_paragraph: The Jets have capitalized on running back Bilal Powell’s ability to produce while giving Shonn Greene a breather, especially in the final month of the regular season.

headline.seo: Bilal Powell Earns Bigger Role in Jets’ Running Game
headline.main: For Jets Offense Built for Run After Run, Powell Provides a Second Wind
